{"id":172315,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/https-everywhere-1-0正式版发布/","date":"2011-08-15T17:31:28Z","modified":"2011-08-15T17:31:28Z","title":"HTTPS Everywhere 1.0正式版发布","content":"<p><p>来源：<a href=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/172ee883/l/0Linternet0Bsolidot0Borg0Carticle0Bpl0Dsid0F110C0A80C0A60C0A7592330Gamp0Pfrom0Frss/story01.htm\">http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/172ee883/l/0Linternet0Bsolidot0Borg0Carticle0Bpl0Dsid0F110C0A80C0A60C0A7592330Gamp0Pfrom0Frss/story01.htm</a>  </p>\n<p>电子前哨基金会(EFF)和Tor项目合作开发的Firefox扩展HTTPS Everywhere 发布了1.0正式版。该扩展旨在阻断搜索劫持和改进Web安全。 HTTPS Everywhere在2010年6月发布了一个测试版，1.0正式版支持超过1000个网站，让用户使用HTTPS加密连接浏览内容。HTTPS协议可 以解决许多网络安全和隐私问题。如果不使用HTTPS，用户的网络行迹容易遭窃听，帐号容易被劫持。1.0版本支持加密Google Image Search、Flickr、Netflix、Apple、NPR、Economist、Google Search、Facebook、Twitter、Hotmail、Wikipedia、 New York Times等流行网站。不过在中国，许多加密连接都被屏蔽了。</p>\n<p>  <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/xijie.wordpress.com/4932/\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg